net.openhft.fix.include.util

Class FixMessagePool.FixMessageContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.openhft.fix.include.util.FixMessagePool.FixMessageContainer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    FixMessagePool

    public static class FixMessagePool.FixMessageContainer
extends Object
implements Externalizable
    Static Inner class used as a container for FixMessage objects. This is used for maintaining the state of the FixMessage Object's state. The state of a FixMessage object can be either in-use OR available.
